paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted information on KCNH2 variant rs1805123 and its association with sudden cardiac death.

key_quotes: The dominant model showed that rs1805123 in KCNH2 was not significantly related to the incidence of SCD (OR: 0.91; 95% CI: 0.75–1.12; P = .487).

challenges: Limited information on individual-level penetrance data for KCNH2 variants.
extraction_metadata.notes: Only one variant in KCNH2 was mentioned, with no detailed penetrance or individual-level data provided.
